                        <note>Ḥusayl (1) and Ribāb (2)’s daughter, Saʿd (5), Mudlij (1) and Safwān (1), Ḥudhayfa (1)’s sister, Thābit (1)’s wife, ʿUmar (17)’s mother</note>
